The '58-'67 parts book at the doc project lists just one part number,
211 501 201, for both axles, but also says "see Workshop Bulletin."
The '54 parts book lists 211 501 127 for both axles.  Unfortunately
there isn't an online parts book that covers '55-'57 in detail.  The
new '50-'62 Bentley doesn't spell out the differences either, as near
as I can tell.

